{"tid":1405800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一地豬嘴 頭盔","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:24:37.000Z","uid":31646,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d03a7e7802c17b277d8e587ffd46b358cf42e97","tid":1405800,"uid":31646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"喂 香港人<br />\n我想見到一地豬嘴 頭盔多過呢堆垃圾卷<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句 呢啲卷衰撚過你放現金<br />\n真正有需要既係裝備 雖然我知依家周圍都無貨<br />\n但你放一堆垃圾卷出黎<span style=\"color: red;\">幫唔到</span>任何有心出力既香港人<br />\n有心既 只能夠幫你兌返現金再買裝備<br />\n依家會拎啲卷既只有貪心大陸人<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀  仆你個街香港人唔係乞衣<br />\n屌你咁樣放落地 你想邊個去拎<br />\n你要幫手 你親手交比附近既人 已經好好<br />\n仲要放啲爛鬼EDO餅 你自己都唔食啦<br />\n可唔可以當手足係自己仔女 比啲好啲既野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mg2RGhh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmg2RGhh.jpg&h=5d0adfb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdwK1qi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdwK1qi.png&h=b7f59198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片轉至隔離post）"},{"pid":"713aa0a3e340736094d3403094c067e6b0259df9","tid":1405800,"uid":210254,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"人地都係有心先出錢買<br />\n你用詞可唔可以好少少？"},{"pid":"18f82ac610ccb0ebb425d145e9ef7187b8c6b432","tid":1405800,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【長輩片】</span><br />\n為藍絲長輩而設既Youtube頻道正式面世！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD0RsaWOAv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCD0RsaWOAv4&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=22eba730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD0RsaWOAv4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【頻道連結】</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Ffreehongkong&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=1df34c9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/freehongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝會員「𢭃住中場」（#283968）設立頻道。<br />\n小弟只係幫手宣傳，希幫各位巴絲多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">------------------【原Po】------------------</span></strong><br />\n全靠黑警！終於搵到方法搞掂中立/藍絲屋企人，唔再嘈交！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvwHpT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvwHpT</a></div>"},{"pid":"21c3194f28870f30c2aac58478ff3dfda358386e","tid":1405800,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"覺得冇問題，反而驚有心人拎走哂"},{"pid":"f663cb2840b3de1ae54d8ab2361e6bff66cdcc48","tid":1405800,"uid":65526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"而家係有錢都未必買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗屌嘅"},{"pid":"bef204c52eb097871de66dee3547c6d0aeb1584e","tid":1405800,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"贖罪劵 買完放低當出左力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884fc4022a8c52833e02cd9638cca75198732df4","tid":1405800,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />裝點會隨地擺呀on9<br />\n會有手足到場派架啦<br />\n唔好亂屌啦好心"},{"pid":"aa4bab5d8cd5b73b8ce494073dee6820287e2639","tid":1405800,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"講多次<br />\n屌你老母呀<br />\n成日屌屌屌<br />\n自己見唔到就屌人<br />\n開個post屌人有幾難？<br />\n但知唔知總有人係背後付出緊？"},{"pid":"eb69e9309029d74af8e8b4741c8850f2f9cac53a","tid":1405800,"uid":105253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"吊咩野呀 人地都係好心姐 買